
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Andrii Pelekh | About Me";
}

<div class="body about">
    <div class="center">
        <div class="left">

            <div class="half">
                <h2>about <span class="dark2">me</span></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="half">
                <div class="padder empty">

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="half">
                <img class="ternopil" src="~/Content/img/ternopil.png">
            </div>
            <div class="half">
                <p>Originally, I am from Ukraine and I have spent most of my life in a beautiful town where I was born called Ternopil.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="half">
                <p>I am a very curious person. I had only one word in my vocabulary when I was a child: "Why?" Most of the time, my never ending questions to my parents or family members ended up with the phrase: "Because I said so".</p>
            </div>
            <div class="half">
                <img class="factory" src="~/Content/img/factory.jpg">
            </div>
            <div class="half">
                <img class="ships" src="~/Content/img/ships.jpg">
            </div>
            <div class="half clear">
                <p>I visited many different places while I was working on cruise ships. Without any doubt, I will never forget hurricane Sandy and those two days at sea when we were trying to avoid it.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="half">
                <p>My previous work experience is in the finance field where I acquired strong problem solving skills, high attention to detail and the ability to take responsibility and achieve results.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="half">
                <img class="finance" src="~/Content/img/finance.jpg">
            </div>
            <div class="half">
                <img class="code" src="~/Content/img/code.jpg">
            </div>
            <div class="half clear">
                <p>I am very passionate about programming and I am thrilled that I decided to gear my career towards this field. Regardless what my future holds, it has been the best decision of my life.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

